{"type": "article", "id": 26014, "title": "蓝牙音箱", "description": "", "date": "2016-04-27T07:19:30Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 400262, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 22, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160702145811arsTAX5lH2LmZGuP.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p class=\"\">这款蓝牙音箱名为 <a href=\"http://www.muemma.com/collections/all/products/arina-speaker-gainsboro-set\" target=\"_blank\">ARiNA</a>，由柏林 MUEMMA 旗下的设计师设计，外观让人联想到苹果公司在美国加州库比蒂诺市（Cupertino）那个酷似飞碟的新总部 Campus2。音箱内部装有 6 个扩音器，可以实现 360 度的环绕音效。值得一提的是，音箱外套还提供了几种颜色和材质供用户更换，在不使用的时候还可以在中间放上手机，当作一个小摆设。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607021458094IylLdRWxXq0H3Tz.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702145809U0qKXvJaiMlNjg9d.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702145810fr0JHPpyjGSo3Bcz.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.93\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702145810E3GyUVcNDxkM1fX7.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n\n"}